725002f-b.title: Queens: 11th Avenue - 150th Street
725002f-b.text:
11th Avenue, adjoining the S. W. corner of 150th Street,
showing the Immanuel Evangelical Lutheran Church. 11th
Avenue was previously called 21st Street.
P. L- Sperr  View 1: April 13, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIIS  View 2: March 5, 1932
